      <title>马斯克寻求前宾夕法尼亚州民主党人支持特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/musk-looks-for-trump-votes-among-former-pennsylvania-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克和唐纳德·特朗普的其他盟友正在努力利用竞争对手卡马拉·哈里斯的“蓝墙”的漏洞：过去十年来，数以千计的宾夕法尼亚州选民已经远离了她的民主党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/musk-looks-for-trump-votes-among-former-pennsylvania-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯在农民强烈反对后为遗产税上调辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/reeves-defends-inheritance-tax-rise-after-backlash-from-farmers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯为她向将农业财产传给子女的英国土地所有者征收遗产税的举措进行辩护，此前批评人士称此举将损害该行业并导致家庭农场的解体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/reeves-defends-inheritance-tax-rise-after-backlash-from-farmers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 14:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
